This app enables direct communication with ChatGPT from your device. The communication generated by the app does not pass through any intermediate servers before reaching ChatGPT.

However, please note that your email address will be shared with ChatGPT along with your requests for usage monitoring. For more information about the data privacy practices of ChatGPT, please refer to their privacy policy available at the following link: ChatGPT Privacy Policy: https://openai.com/policies/privacy-policy

The app also uses Google Firebase for login. Please review the Google Firebase Privacy and Data Security Policy below: https://firebase.google.com/support/privacy

The app does not save or share the request itself or the response from ChatGPT with any party except ChatGPT.

We also confirm that the app collects the following information and saves it to the Google Firebase Database to help us improve the app and monitor the costs associated with ChatGPT usage:

Your email address
The token used to process your request from ChatGPT. The tokens are in the form of numbers and help us calculate the cost of your request.
The time you sent the message.
We hereby state, to the best of our knowledge and belief, that we have not programmed this app to collect any further personal information. You can delete all of your messages by simply uninstalling the application.

To provide the functionality of saving and loading images and files, the app requires access to your device's storage. This access is necessary solely for the purpose of managing these specific app-related files.

It's important to note that the app contacts ChatGPT via an API over HTTPS, ensuring that the communication is encrypted for enhanced security and privacy.

Please review and familiarize yourself with this privacy policy. If you have any concerns or questions regarding the privacy of your data, please feel free to contact us.

The App require the following permissions:
    <uses-permission android:name="android.permission.INTERNET" />
    <uses-permission android:name="android.permission.ACCESS_NETWORK_STATE" />
    <uses-permission android:name="android.permission.WRITE_EXTERNAL_STORAGE" />
    
    <uses-permission android:name="android.permission.INTERNET" />
     to Access ChatGPT directly 
    <uses-permission android:name="android.permission.ACCESS_NETWORK_STATE" />
      To check network connectivty and informs you when there is an issue with internet connectivity 
      
    <uses-permission android:name="android.permission.WRITE_EXTERNAL_STORAGE" />
      To save images and files generated by the app on local storage    
        
